									Sub-Inspector (Executive) in Delhi Police &#8211; (Male/Female): Joining Delhi
									Police as a Sub-Inspector (Executive) involves serving the capital city and
									maintaining law and order, ensuring safety for the citizens.<span
										style="color: #000000;"><strong><br />
											<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Short
													Information:</strong></span></strong></span> The staff selection
									commission (SSC) has released the SSC CPO 2023 Recruitment <a
										href="https://www.sarkariresult.app/latest-jobs/">Delhi Police CPO SI
										Notification</a> for the posts of Sub-Inspector (SI) in Central Armed Police
									Forces (CAPFs) and Sub-Inspector (SI) in Delhi Police including the CRPF, BSF, ITBP,
									CISF, SSB. The objective of the <a
										href="https://www.sarkariresult.app/rojgar-result/">SSC CPO recruitment</a>
									drive is to fill vacancies for various 1876 posts in various categories through the
									SSC CPO SI online application process. Eligible candidates should apply for SSC CPO
									posts through online mode only through the official website of SSC ssc.nic.in.
									Applicants should read the conditions given in the Delhi Police Bharti notification
									to apply.</p>
